<!-- 定義及症狀 -->
'''路易氏體失智症'''（{{lang-en|Dementia with Lewy bodies}}，縮寫為 DLB）是一種伴隨著{{le|行為變化|Behavior change (individual)|行為}}、[[認知|認知]]及{{le|巴金森症候群|Parkinsonism|活動功能退化}}的[[失智症|失智症]]<ref name=McKeithConsensus2017/>，患者的記憶力雖不見得在罹病初期就會衰退<ref name=Tousi2017>{{cite journal |vauthors=Tousi B |title=Diagnosis and management of cognitive and behavioral changes in dementia with Lewy bodies |journal=Curr Treat Options Neurol |volume=19 |issue=11 |page=42 |date=October 2017 |pmid=28990131 |doi=10.1007/s11940-017-0478-x |type=Review}}</ref>，但失智的情形還是會{{le|進行性疾病|Progressive disease|隨著時間逐漸惡化}}<ref name=Weil2017>{{cite journal |vauthors=Weil RS, Lashley TL, Bras J, Schrag AE, Schott JM |title=Current concepts and controversies in the pathogenesis of Parkinson's disease dementia and dementia with Lewy bodies |journal=F1000Res |volume=6 |page=1604 |date=2017 |pmid=28928962 |pmc=5580419 |doi=10.12688/f1000research.11725.1 |type=Review}}</ref>，通常是當患者的認知功能退化到影響[[日常生活活動|日常生活]]，之後接受檢查而確診<ref name=McKeithConsensus2017/><ref name=StLouisNov2017/>。。此症的主要特徵之一是{{le|動眼期睡眠行為障礙|REM Behavioral Disorder}}（RBD），患者在[[動眼期|動眼期]]應出現的{{le|肌失張|Atony}}並未出現，反而會出現反應夢境之行為表現<ref name=McKeithConsensus2017/>；此障礙可能較其他症狀提早數年甚至數十年就發生<ref name=StLouisMay2017>{{cite journal |vauthors=St Louis EK, Boeve AR, Boeve BF |title=REM sleep behavior disorder in Parkinson's disease and other synucleinopathies |journal=Mov Disord |volume=32 |issue=5 |pages=645–58 |date=May 2017 |pmid=28513079 |doi=10.1002/mds.27018|type=Review }}</ref>。其他常見的症狀包括出現[[幻覺|幻覺]]、[[注意力|注意力]]的起伏不定及[[運動功能減退症|行動遲緩]]、步態不穩或[[運動功能減退症|運動功能減退]]<ref name=McKeithConsensus2017/>。患者的自主神经紊乱自主神經系統通常也會受到[[自主神经紊乱|影響]]，導致[[姿位性低血壓|血壓]]、心臟及消化道功能改變，並且常常[[便秘|便秘]]<ref name=Palma2018>{{cite journal |vauthors=Palma JA, Kaufmann H |title=Treatment of autonomic dysfunction in Parkinson disease and other synucleinopathies |journal=Mov Disord |volume=33 |issue=3 |pages=372–90 |date=March 2018 |pmid=29508455 |doi=10.1002/mds.27344 |type=Review}}</ref> ；此外像是變的[[抑鬱|抑鬱]]及對人[[冷漠|冷漠]]等情緒轉變也很常見<ref name=McKeithConsensus2017/>。

<!-- 病因及診斷 -->
目前還無法確定路易氏體失智症的確切原因<ref name=NINDS2017>{{cite web |title= Dementia with Lewy bodies information page |publisher= National Institute of Neurological Disorders and Stroke |url= https://www.ninds.nih.gov/Disorders/All-Disorders/Dementia-Lewy-Bodies-Information-Page |accessdate= April 7, 2018 |date= May 25, 2017 |archive-date= 2021-06-10 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20210610102946/https://www.ninds.nih.gov/Disorders/All-Disorders/Dementia-Lewy-Bodies-Information-Page |dead-url= no }}</ref>，不過和神經中{{le|α-突觸核蛋白|Alpha-synuclein}}異常團塊的廣泛沉積有關，這種沈積稱為{{le|路易氏體|Lewy bodies}}或路易氏突起（Lewy neurites）<ref name=Walker2015>{{cite journal |vauthors=Walker Z, Possin KL, Boeve BF, Aarsland D |title=Lewy body dementias |journal=Lancet |volume=386 |issue=10004 |pages=1683–97 |date=October 2015 |pmid=26595642 |pmc=5792067 |doi=10.1016/S0140-6736(15)00462-6 |type=Review}}</ref><ref name=Velayudhan2017>{{cite journal |vauthors=Velayudhan L, Ffytche D, Ballard C, Aarsland D |title=New therapeutic strategies for Lewy body dementias |journal=Curr Neurol Neurosci Rep |volume=17 |issue=9 |page=68 |date=September 2017 |pmid=28741230 |doi=10.1007/s11910-017-0778-2 |type=Review}}</ref>。一般而言，路易氏體失智症不是遺傳的，不過也有少數家庭的路易氏體失智症和基因有關<ref name=NINDS2017/>。可能性的診斷會以其症狀以及[[生物标记|生物标记]]來判斷，診斷會包括[[血液检查|血液检查]]、{{le|神經心理學測試|neuropsychological tests}}、[[醫學影像|醫學影像]]及[[多項生理睡眠檢查|多項生理睡眠檢查]]<ref name=McKeithConsensus2017/><ref name=NINDS2017Book/>。其他[[鑑別診斷|會有類似症狀的疾病]]有[[阿茲海默症|阿茲海默症]]、[[帕金森氏症|帕金森氏症]]、[[譫妄|譫妄]]，偶爾[[思覺失調|思覺失調]]也會有類似症狀<ref name=Tousi2017/>。

<!-- 預防及治療 -->
目前沒有治愈方法或藥物會改變疾病的進展<ref name=NINDS2017/>。這種病現行的治療旨在緩解一些症狀<ref name=NINDS2017/> 並減輕照顧者的負擔<ref name=StLouisNov2017>{{cite journal |vauthors=St Louis EK, Boeve BF |title=REM sleep behavior disorder: Diagnosis, clinical implications, and future directions |journal=Mayo Clin Proc |volume=92 |issue=11 |pages=1723–36 |date=November 2017 |pmid=29101940 |doi=10.1016/j.mayocp.2017.09.007 |type=Review |url=http://www.mayoclinicproceedings.org/article/S0025-6196(17)30688-2/fulltext |access-date=2018-12-03 |archive-date=2021-07-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210720105427/https://www.mayoclinicproceedings.org/article/S0025-6196%2817%2930688-2/fulltext |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=Mueller2017>{{cite journal |vauthors=Mueller C, Ballard C, Corbett A, Aarsland D |title=The prognosis of dementia with Lewy bodies |journal=Lancet Neurol |volume=16 |issue=5 |pages=390–98 |date=May 2017 |pmid=28342649 |doi=10.1016/S1474-4422(17)30074-1|type=Review}}</ref><ref name=Boot2013>{{cite journal |vauthors=Boot BP, McDade EM, McGinnis SM, Boeve BF |title=Treatment of dementia with Lewy bodies |journal=Curr Treat Options Neurol |volume=15 |issue=6 |pages=738–64 |date=December 2013 |pmid=24222315 |pmc=3913181 |doi=10.1007/s11940-013-0261-6 |type=Review}}</ref>。{{le|乙酰膽鹼酯酶抑制劑|Acetylcholinesterase inhibitor}}（AChEI）如{{le|donepezil|donepezil}}和{{le|rivastigmine|rivastigmine}}，可有效改善認知和整體功能，[[褪黑激素|褪黑激素]]則可用於睡眠相關症狀<ref name=McKeithConsensus2017>{{cite journal |vauthors=McKeith IG, Boeve BF, Dickson DW, ''et al'' |title=Diagnosis and management of dementia with Lewy bodies: Fourth consensus report of the DLB Consortium |journal=Neurology |volume=89 |issue=1 |pages=88–100 |date=July 2017 |pmid=28592453 |pmc=5496518 |doi=10.1212/WNL.0000000000004058 |type=Review }}</ref>。即使有幻覺，患有DLB的人也會避免使用[[抗精神病藥物|抗精神病藥物]]，因為患者對這類藥物很敏感<ref name=McKeithConsensus2017/>，若使用可能導致死亡<ref name=Boot2015>{{cite journal |vauthors=Boot BP |title=Comprehensive treatment of dementia with Lewy bodies |journal=Alzheimers Res Ther |volume=7 |issue=1 |page=45 |date=2015 |pmid=26029267 |pmc=4448151 |doi=10.1186/s13195-015-0128-z |type=Review}}</ref>。特定症狀的藥物也可能會使另一種症狀惡化<ref name=Walker2015/>。

<!-- 流行病學及預後 -->
路易氏體失智症是常見失智症中的一種，另外二種是[[阿茲海默症|阿茲海默症]]及[[血管性痴呆|血管性痴呆]]<ref name=NINDS2017Book/><ref name=Kosakav>Kosaka K, ed. (2017), p. v.</ref>{{efn|name=CommonDem|Kosaka (2017) writes: "Dementia with Lewy bodies (DLB) is now well known to be the second most frequent dementia following Alzheimer disease (AD). Of all types of dementia, AD is known to account for about 50%, DLB about 20% and vascular dementia (VD) about 15%. Thus, AD, DLB, and VD are now considered to be the three major dementias."<ref name=Kosakav/> The NINDS (2017) says that Lewy body dementia "is one of the most common causes of dementia, after Alzheimer’s disease and vascular disease."<ref name=NINDS2017Book>{{cite web |title= Lewy body dementia: Hope through research |url= https://www.ninds.nih.gov/Disorders/Patient-Caregiver-Education/Hope-Through-Research/Lewy-Body-Dementia-Hope-Through-Research |website= National Institute of Neurological Disorders and Stroke |publisher= US National Institutes of Health |accessdate= April 6, 2018 |date= December 8, 2017 |archive-date= 2021-04-30 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20210430175606/https://www.ninds.nih.gov/Disorders/Patient-Caregiver-Education/Hope-Through-Research/Lewy-Body-Dementia-Hope-Through-Research |dead-url= no }}</ref>}}。路易氏體失智症通常發生在50歲以後，且大約0.4%的人65歲後會罹患此疾病<ref name= Levin2016>{{cite journal |vauthors=Levin J, Kurz A, Arzberger T, Giese A, Höglinger GU |title=The differential diagnosis and treatment of atypical parkinsonism |journal=Dtsch Arztebl Int |volume=113 |issue=5 |pages=61–69 |date=February 2016 |pmid=26900156 |pmc=4782269 |doi=10.3238/arztebl.2016.0061 | type=Review}}</ref>，疾病晚期，患者將無法照顧自己<ref name=NIH2017Bas>{{cite web |title= What is Lewy body dementia? |url= https://www.nia.nih.gov/alzheimers/publication/lewy-body-dementia/basics-lewy-body-dementia |website= National Institute on Aging |publisher= US National Institutes of Health |accessdate= April 7, 2018 |date= May 17, 2017 |archive-date= 2016-10-06 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20161006063420/https://www.nia.nih.gov/alzheimers/publication/lewy-body-dementia/basics-lewy-body-dementia |dead-url= no }}</ref>，確診後[[預期壽命|預期壽命]]約8年<ref name=NINDS2017/>不正常的蛋白質沉積機制於1912年由{{le|Frederic Lewy|Frederic Lewy}}發現，而首次路易氏體失智症則在1976年由{{le|小阪憲司|Kenji Kosaka}}記錄<ref name=Weil2017/>。

